            </div>

            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-image" style="background-image: url('https://source.unsplash.com/random/300x200/?comedy');">
                    <span class="event-badge">Hot</span>
                </div>
                <div class="event-details">
                    <h3>Comedy Night Special</h3>
                    <div class="event-meta">
                        <span class="event-date">May 25, 2024</span>
                        <span class="event-location">Laugh Factory, LA</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>An unforgettable night of laughter with the funniest comedians.</p>
                    <div class="event-footer">
                        <span class="event-price">From $49</span>
